org.apache.juneau.rest.client2

Class RestResponseStatusLineAssertion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.assertions.Assertion
      • org.apache.juneau.assertions.FluentAssertion<RestResponse>
        • org.apache.juneau.rest.client2.RestResponseStatusLineAssertion

  • public class RestResponseStatusLineAssertion
extends FluentAssertion<RestResponse>
    Used for fluent assertion calls against a response StatusLine object.
    Example:

    // Validates the response status code is 200 or 404. client .get(URI) .run() .assertStatus().code().isAny(200,404);
